0" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Hayley-Williams-and-Chappel-Roan.-Credit-Gregor-Fischer-and-Josh-Brasted-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="海莉·威廉姆斯和查普尔·罗恩。图片来源：Gregor Fischer 和 Josh Brasted，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Hayley-Williams-and-Chappel-Roan.-Credit-Gregor-Fischer-and-Josh-Brasted-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Hayley-Williams-and-Chappel-Roan.-Credit-Gregor-Fischer-and-Josh-Brasted-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Hayley-Williams-and-Chappel-Roan.-Credit-Gregor-Fischer-and-Josh-Brasted-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Hayley-Williams-and-Chappel-Roan.-Credit-Gregor-Fischer-and-Josh-Brasted-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Hayley-Williams-and-Chappel-Roan.-Credit-Gregor-Fischer-and-Josh-Brasted-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Hayley-Williams-and-Chappel-Roan.-Credit-Gregor-Fischer-and-Josh-Brasted-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Paramore">Paramore</a>的<a href="/aritsts/Hayley-Williams">海莉·威廉姆斯 (Hayley Williams)</a>公开谈论了<a href="/aritsts/Chappell-Roan">查普尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan</a> ) 的粉丝界限评论，她认为这种评论“勇敢”且“不幸的是有必要”。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="462" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-chapell-roan-interview-the-rise-and-fall-of-a-midwest-princess-3582467"><b>Chappell Roan：流行超新星，感觉就像“变装皇后”女孩之一</b></a></li></ul><p>这位“Hot To Go”歌手上周末（8月24日）在她的社交媒体上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-writes-to-superfans-about-predatory-behaviour-women-dont-owe-you-shit-3786492">发帖，针对所谓“超级粉丝”的“掠夺行为”，强调“女人不欠你狗屎”。</a></p><p> “这不是集体谈话，”她说。这篇文章指出，经过十年的职业生涯建设，“我已经到了需要划清界限、设定界限的地步了。”</p><p> “我经历了太多未经同意的身体和社交互动，我只是需要把它列出来并提醒你，女人不欠你狗屎，”她写道。 “我选择这条职业道路是因为我热爱音乐和艺术，尊重我内心的童真，我不接受任何形式的骚扰，因为我选择了这条道路，我也不值得。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_CGxsrP4Bc/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560